- It depends on you.

37
00:02:47,481 --> 00:02:49,180
- Me?
- Yes.

38
00:02:49,180 --> 00:02:52,214
As for the app, I have asked Brother Yingjun to do a launch test.

39
00:02:52,214 --> 00:02:55,948
Xiaoting and Chen Han will complete uploading the customer's data and documents.

40
00:02:55,948 --> 00:02:59,814
