68
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,148
Facing south, come on.

69
00:04:23,148 --> 00:04:25,680
- Come on.
- Let's buy it!

70
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,180
- Meng Heng.
- Wait for me.

71
00:04:27,180 --> 00:04:29,048
- I still have more.
- I also have more.

72
00:04:29,048 --> 00:04:30,415
Meng Heng, here.

73
00:04:30,415 --> 00:04:32,448
What are you all doing?

74
00:04:33,748 --> 00:04:36,115
Selling houses.

75
00:04:39,614 --> 00:04:42,147
And what are you doing?

76
00:04:42,147 --> 00:04:43,948
I'm building performance.

77
00:04:43,948 --> 00:04:45,648
Building performance?

78
00:04:45,648 --> 00:04:48,847
I thought, with your proposal and these performances,

79
00:04:48,847 --> 00:04:52,048
the president wouldn't trouble our sales department anymore.

80
00:04:53,415 --> 00:04:54,915
Where did you get the money?

81
00:04:54,915 --> 00:04:56,915
I borrowed.

82
00:04:56,915 --> 00:04:58,015
You haven't graduated yet.

83
00:04:58,015 --> 00:04:59,847
How could the bank lend you so much money?

84
00:04:59,847 --> 00:05:01,248
It's not borrowed from the bank.

85
00:05:01,248 --> 00:05:03,548
It is… private lending.

86
00:05:03,548 --> 00:05:07,348
You borrowed from a loan shark? Are you crazy?

87
00:05:07,348 --> 00:05:09,180
It's one thing if he's crazy, but what about you adults?

88
00:05:09,180 --> 00:05:12,047
- How old is he, and how old are you?
- Calm down.

89
00:05:12,047 --> 00:05:15,615
Meng Heng borrowed money from his mother.

90
00:05:16,481 --> 00:05:17,915
Meng Heng's mother?

91
00:05:17,915 --> 00:05:19,814
Didn't you know?

92
00:05:19,814 --> 00:05:21,915
He's a hidden second-generation rich kid.

93
00:05:21,915 --> 00:05:23,381
Yeah.

94
00:05:23,381 --> 00:05:26,981
If Fen from Taiyao Construction last month didn't recognize Meng Heng,

95
00:05:26,981 --> 00:05:29,214
we wouldn't have known that Meng Heng's mother

96
00:05:29,214 --> 00:05:30,882
is a super client of Taiyao Construction.

97
00:05:30,882 --> 00:05:34,580
Occupation: Landlady.

98
00:05:37,915 --> 00:05:40,014
So annoying, she's constantly calling.

99
00:05:40,014 --> 00:05:41,682
[Landlady]
She's been calling all day, constantly calling.

100
00:05:41,682 --> 00:05:44,315
Help me smash it.

101
00:05:50,082 --> 00:05:52,448
So that "landlady" is your mother?

102
00:05:52,448 --> 00:05:54,714
I just don't want to live off collecting rent.

103
00:05:54,714 --> 00:05:55,815
It's so boring.

104
00:05:55,815 --> 00:05:58,015
So I had an argument with my mother.

105
00:05:58,015 --> 00:05:59,714
I wanted to rely on myself.

106
00:05:59,714 --> 00:06:01,782
Rely on yourself, but you still borrowed money from her.

107
00:06:01,782 --> 00:06:04,848
Wait. It's different.

108
00:06:04,848 --> 00:06:06,947
Borrowing money means paying it back.

109
00:06:06,947 --> 00:06:08,715
He's still relying on himself.

110
00:06:08,715 --> 00:06:12,148
Besides, her profession is a landlady.

111
00:06:12,148 --> 00:06:14,181
She needs properties to collect rent.

112
00:06:14,181 --> 00:06:17,414
Meng Heng doing this is also filial.

113
00:06:17,414 --> 00:06:19,014
Exactly.

114
00:06:19,014 --> 00:06:20,881
Besides, ever since I started my internship at Jingdu Construction,

115
00:06:20,881 --> 00:06:24,347
I realized that whether it's the location, the environment,

116
00:06:24,347 --> 00:06:27,247
the selection of building materials, or the layout and design,

117
00:06:27,247 --> 00:06:28,948
it's all very good.

118
00:06:28,948 --> 00:06:31,481
Our company also accomplishes the sustainable housing service concept.

119
00:06:31,481 --> 00:06:34,014
Whether it's for self-occupancy or investment, it's very suitable.

120
00:06:34,014 --> 00:06:36,213
That's absolutely right.

121
00:06:36,213 --> 00:06:37,881
I've also seen those house layouts.

122
00:06:37,881 --> 00:06:40,582
When I went to the site with Brother Yingjun before, I had already seen it.

123
00:06:40,582 --> 00:06:42,581
I'm not buying it randomly.

124
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:46,681
If that's the case, it really doesn't seem to be a problem.

125
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,248
Cindy.

126
00:06:53,113 --> 00:06:57,047
Meng Heng, actually, I also have a few units in my hand. Large luxury houses.

127
00:06:57,047 --> 00:06:59,481
- You can consider it.
- Gao Shuangyun!

128
00:06:59,481 --> 00:07:02,247
- Meng Heng.
- Queue up.

129
00:07:02,247 --> 00:07:04,015
Manager, I trust your experience.

130
00:07:04,015 --> 00:07:05,580
Let's buy them!

131
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:06,947
Congratulations.

132
00:07:06,947 --> 00:07:08,347
Mine, hurry up.

133
00:07:08,347 --> 00:07:09,981
- Mine is here, hurry, quickly.
- Sensible.

134
00:07:09,981 --> 00:07:11,947
