135
00:07:14,814 --> 00:07:16,580
Fu, sorry I'm late.

136
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:18,015
It's okay, please sit.

137
00:07:18,015 --> 00:07:19,396
Okay.

138
00:07:21,847 --> 00:07:23,815
