142
00:07:29,582 --> 00:07:32,815
- Do you have anything you want?
- I can eat anything.

143
00:07:32,815 --> 00:07:36,513
I've ordered for you the best thing from this restaurant.

144
00:07:37,747 --> 00:07:42,248
You know? Meng Heng is a second-generation rich kid.

145
00:07:43,450 --> 00:07:44,480
So what?

146
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,815
I didn't think much of it at first,

147
00:07:46,815 --> 00:07:50,980
but I heard that Meng Heng helps the sales department achieve performance by buying properties.

148
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:53,080
- With him in the sales department like this…
- Don't worry.

149
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,915
How much can he buy alone?

150
00:07:54,915 --> 00:07:56,714
No matter what the sales department does,

151
00:07:56,714 --> 00:07:59,580
it's all just a desperate struggle.

152
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:01,280
Okay.

153
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:03,313
- Hello, here is your meal.
- Come.

154
00:08:03,313 --> 00:08:05,013
Thank you.

155
00:08:05,013 --> 00:08:06,980
Thank you. Everything is here, enjoy your meal.

156
00:08:06,980 --> 00:08:08,213
Thank you.

157
00:08:08,213 --> 00:08:10,347
This is all we've ordered for the two of us?

158
00:08:10,347 --> 00:08:13,548
For dinner, let me tell you. For dinner,

159
00:08:13,548 --> 00:08:16,313
