160
00:08:16,313 --> 00:08:18,980
Come, let's split it in half.

161
00:08:20,247 --> 00:08:21,781
Here.

162
00:08:28,782 --> 00:08:33,248
Also, I think we should make a proposal to the boss.

163
00:08:33,248 --> 00:08:36,281
After all, we are the planning department. We are doing planning.

164
00:08:36,281 --> 00:08:40,915
We can make a proposal to enhance customer service.

165
00:08:40,915 --> 00:08:45,080
All the measures you just mentioned are just four words,

166
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,981
superficial but not practical.

167
00:08:47,981 --> 00:08:51,914
- No, but I just—
- I'm telling you, please, don't worry.

168
00:08:51,914 --> 00:08:56,613
Now the sales department can't even see our taillights.

169
00:09:03,313 --> 00:09:04,948
Aren't you eating?

170
00:09:06,614 --> 00:09:08,648
Don't waste it.

171
00:09:08,648 --> 00:09:12,248
Those who waste will end up in hell.

172
00:09:13,347 --> 00:09:15,048
I'll save you.

173
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:22,072
[A new message]

174
00:09:26,882 --> 00:09:30,013
Sister Chen said the president wants everyone to have a meeting tomorrow morning.

175
00:09:30,013 --> 00:09:32,747
Each department should prepare their main business and proposals.

176
00:09:32,747 --> 00:09:35,447
8:30 a.m. in the conference room.

177
00:09:38,914 --> 00:09:40,848
Yes.

178
00:09:40,848 --> 00:09:46,580
Tomorrow is the day I become the vice president.

179
00:09:48,047 --> 00:09:51,514
Quickly, let's hurry back to the office and prepare for tomorrow.

180
00:09:51,514 --> 00:09:54,447
Waiter. Check, please.

181
00:09:57,047 --> 00:09:59,682
Hello, today's bill is TWD$848.

182
00:09:59,682 --> 00:10:02,715
- This is your cash voucher.
- Okay.

183
00:10:02,715 --> 00:10:03,715
I just calculated it.

184
00:10:03,715 --> 00:10:05,414
There's still some change, probably just a few dozen dollars.

185
00:10:05,414 --> 00:10:07,048
It's your turn.

186
00:10:07,048 --> 00:10:09,415
Still $148 short.

187
00:10:09,415 --> 00:10:12,781
Hurry and pay up. There's still work at the company.

188
00:10:13,714 --> 00:10:15,780
Becoming the vice president.

189
00:10:18,414 --> 00:10:20,848
Still $148 short.

190
00:10:24,013 --> 00:10:27,448
Anyway, our collaboration with Xin Daqi is not just about the building project.

191
00:10:27,448 --> 00:10:30,981
We also have a resort and a wellness village.

192
00:10:30,981 --> 00:10:32,981
Wherever the excavator can reach, we will go.

193
00:10:32,981 --> 00:10:35,680
Where the excavator cannot reach, we will pave the way

194
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:37,281
and plant Jingdu's flag there.

195
00:10:37,281 --> 00:10:41,014
We want Jingdu's buildings to cover the whole world.

196
00:10:44,813 --> 00:10:46,080
Very good.

197
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:49,814
No wonder I heard people say if you want to make big money,

198
00:10:49,814 --> 00:10:52,215
you can't talk about profit first.

199
00:10:52,215 --> 00:10:56,381
You must have a great and beautiful vision.

200
00:10:56,381 --> 00:10:58,048
Right?

201
00:10:58,048 --> 00:11:02,081
Manager Wu, you have such ambition.

202
00:11:02,081 --> 00:11:03,281
Amazing.

203
00:11:03,281 --> 00:11:05,848
Especially after just hearing what he said,

204
00:11:05,848 --> 00:11:10,314
it reminds me of when we used to work hard by the chairman's side.

205
00:11:10,314 --> 00:11:11,982
Don't you agree, Sister Chen?

206
00:11:11,982 --> 00:11:13,148
Yes.

207
00:11:13,148 --> 00:11:17,514
I also think Manager Wu's vision map is particularly big and particularly good.

208
00:11:17,514 --> 00:11:18,648
Very good.

209
00:11:18,648 --> 00:11:19,815
Thank you, Sister Chen.

210
00:11:19,815 --> 00:11:24,314
Under the leadership of the president, my spirit of hard work has never changed.

211
00:11:24,314 --> 00:11:27,415
Grand goals provide the motivation to move forward.

212
00:11:27,415 --> 00:11:29,380
Thank you, President. Thank you.

213
00:11:29,380 --> 00:11:32,213
Okay, sit down. Please sit.

214
00:11:32,213 --> 00:11:34,281
You've worked hard.

215
00:11:34,281 --> 00:11:37,014
Okay, well done, planning department.

216
00:11:37,014 --> 00:11:40,347
Well, Manager Gao,

217
00:11:40,347 --> 00:11:43,214
how is the sales department doing?

218
00:11:43,214 --> 00:11:46,681
The colleagues in the sales department are all working hard to catch up with the performance.

219
00:11:46,681 --> 00:11:49,813
However, we have some ideas that we want to report to you.

220
00:11:49,813 --> 00:11:51,848
Okay, go ahead.

221
00:11:51,848 --> 00:11:56,015
First, let's invite our most beautiful Jingdu ambassador, Aisi.

222
00:11:57,255 --> 00:11:59,594
[Jingdu Customer Care APP]

223
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:04,580
One phone call, a lifetime of protection.

224
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:06,980
I am the Jingdu ambassador, Fang Aisi.

225
00:12:11,148 --> 00:12:14,847
The company's corporate spirit is integrity, love, and sustainability.

226
00:12:14,847 --> 00:12:16,315
To implement sustainability,

227
00:12:16,315 --> 00:12:19,913
we should provide permanent maintenance and sustainable service.

228
00:12:19,913 --> 00:12:21,848
Having this app on one's phone,

229
00:12:21,848 --> 00:12:23,648
customers buying houses from Jingdu

230
00:12:23,648 --> 00:12:26,815
