233
00:12:34,913 --> 00:12:36,481
And it will also be retroactive.

234
00:12:36,481 --> 00:12:39,880
Whether it's a new homeowner or a homeowner from years ago,

235
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:42,248
they can all use this function.

236
00:12:42,248 --> 00:12:44,747
Next, for customers of pre-sale houses,

237
00:12:44,747 --> 00:12:47,314
we also provide real-time reports on construction progress,

238
00:12:47,314 --> 00:12:50,547
so that customers can keep track of their future homes at any time,

239
00:12:50,547 --> 00:12:54,482
watching their future homes being built bit by bit until completion.

240
00:12:54,482 --> 00:12:58,513
I believe this can bring immense happiness to our customers.

241
00:12:59,313 --> 00:13:01,182
That's great.

242
00:13:01,948 --> 00:13:06,814
In the past, we never thought after-sales service could reach this level.

243
00:13:06,814 --> 00:13:10,980
Not bad, really good. Keep going.

244
00:13:10,980 --> 00:13:13,682
Considering the wide age range of home buyers,

245
00:13:13,682 --> 00:13:17,082
some customers like to directly call the repair hotline.

246
00:13:17,082 --> 00:13:19,281
We plan to ask Aisi,

247
00:13:19,281 --> 00:13:21,948
the Jingdu ambassador

248
00:13:21,948 --> 00:13:23,781
who has the sweetest voice and looks,

249
00:13:23,781 --> 00:13:26,447
to be responsible for recording the repair hotline messages.

250
00:13:27,913 --> 00:13:30,981
Wu Tianfu is really a supervillain.

251
00:13:30,981 --> 00:13:32,515
Really, he made so many people angry.

252
00:13:32,515 --> 00:13:33,815
I think this time he…

253
00:13:33,815 --> 00:13:35,314
- Really?
- Cover him with a sack.

254
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:36,781
- What are you discussing?
- Don't worry.

255
00:13:36,781 --> 00:13:38,580
What meeting are you having?

256
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:41,048
Are you thinking that Cindy Wang's strategy

257
00:13:41,048 --> 00:13:43,681
