258
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:47,047
Please, we have great confidence in Sister Cindy, okay?

259
00:13:47,047 --> 00:13:50,815
Yes, we are discussing which restaurant to hold today's celebration party.

260
00:13:50,815 --> 00:13:52,180
That's right.

261
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:56,515
Our action this time, should score 99 points, if not 100.

262
00:13:56,515 --> 00:14:00,280
Besides, we have mobilized royal relatives, our Jingdu ambassador.

263
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:02,848
How could it not win the boss's heart?

264
00:14:02,848 --> 00:14:07,515
I'm telling you, it's simply a sure win.

265
00:14:07,515 --> 00:14:08,447
Really?

266
00:14:08,447 --> 00:14:12,514
Are you up to some bad things again?

267
00:14:13,213 --> 00:14:16,781
Brother Guo, it's never too late to turn back.

268
00:14:18,148 --> 00:14:19,814
You guys…

269
00:14:21,582 --> 00:14:24,613
Why do your sarcastic comments feel so refreshing?

270
00:14:24,613 --> 00:14:27,680
There's a sense of complete relaxation, like being bathed in the spring breeze.

271
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,448
I really want to get back to the sales department to be scolded by you guys.

272
00:14:29,448 --> 00:14:32,413
- Hurry up and scold me.
- You're a masochist. You know what I'm saying?

273
00:14:32,413 --> 00:14:33,481
Masochist.

274
00:14:33,481 --> 00:14:35,647
That's really perverted.

275
00:14:35,647 --> 00:14:37,380
You missed me, right?

276
00:14:37,380 --> 00:14:38,448
- Not really.
- Actually, we're okay.

277
00:14:38,448 --> 00:14:39,781
- It's really okay.
- You're overthinking.

278
00:14:39,781 --> 00:14:41,547
You guys…

279
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:44,114
By the way, where are you going to celebrate later?

280
00:14:44,114 --> 00:14:45,947
- This seat is taken.
- It's Meng Heng's.

281
00:14:45,947 --> 00:14:48,681
- Please go away.
- On the ground.

282
00:14:48,681 --> 00:14:51,215
There's really no colleague love.

283
00:14:57,815 --> 00:14:59,715
Do you want me to get you a cup of hot tea?

284
00:14:59,715 --> 00:15:01,182
I…

285
00:15:06,448 --> 00:15:08,514
Can't you read the room?
[Jingdu Construction Organization]

286
00:15:08,514 --> 00:15:10,481
Do I not look angry enough?

287
00:15:10,481 --> 00:15:13,581
You want me to drink hot tea. Are you trying to make me boil?

288
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:20,348
Actually, it's not that bad.

289
00:15:20,348 --> 00:15:21,747
Besides, your position hasn't changed.

290
00:15:21,747 --> 00:15:25,113
Didn't the boss give you a raise?

291
00:15:25,113 --> 00:15:26,981
Why are you smiling?

292
00:15:26,981 --> 00:15:29,214
I'm asking you, what are you laughing at?

293
00:15:30,148 --> 00:15:32,348
What good is a raise?

294
00:15:33,815 --> 00:15:36,881
How embarrassing was it in the meeting room just now? Did you see it?

295
00:15:37,515 --> 00:15:38,715
In my opinion,

296
00:15:38,715 --> 00:15:41,547
Manager Wu managed to secure the Xin Daqi project

297
00:15:41,547 --> 00:15:44,281
which is highly promising,

298
00:15:44,281 --> 00:15:45,647
is really impressive.

299
00:15:45,647 --> 00:15:47,880
A great achievement.

300
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:49,813
However,

301
00:15:50,315 --> 00:15:54,714
have you neglected your duties?

302
00:15:55,848 --> 00:15:59,148
Look at the sales department. They are so high-profile,

303
00:15:59,148 --> 00:16:01,747
developing an app for sustainable housing.

304
00:16:01,747 --> 00:16:03,682
Also, they've attracted so many members

305
00:16:03,682 --> 00:16:05,913
to apply for membership and download the app.

306
00:16:05,913 --> 00:16:09,080
Have you not noticed at all?

307
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:11,348
You're too slow-witted.

308
00:16:11,348 --> 00:16:13,614
Wu, this won't do.

309
00:16:13,614 --> 00:16:17,815
From the looks of it, you are still not qualified enough

310
00:16:17,815 --> 00:16:20,180
to be a vice president.

311
00:16:25,148 --> 00:16:29,815
Yes, boss. I will definitely reflect on it, reflect on it.

312
00:16:32,981 --> 00:16:38,080
Excuse me. As for the potted plant Manager Wu left in the vice president's office,

313
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:41,247
when it is convenient for you, I'll help you move it back.

314
00:16:42,913 --> 00:16:46,315
Aren't we supposed to prepare the proposal for the boss tomorrow?

315
00:16:46,315 --> 00:16:48,481
How come we're moving things?

316
00:16:48,481 --> 00:16:52,114
Isn't it too early to move now?

317
00:16:52,114 --> 00:16:54,514
Keep your voice down.

318
00:16:54,514 --> 00:16:59,047
We come now just to take advantage of the time when they are sleeping

319
00:16:59,047 --> 00:17:02,314
and let them, and us,

320
00:17:02,314 --> 00:17:05,147
get familiar with the environment together.

321
00:17:08,181 --> 00:17:09,715
No one has been confirmed to be promoted to vice president yet.

322
00:17:09,715 --> 00:17:14,047
Isn't putting things in the office a bit too much?

323
00:17:20,114 --> 00:17:21,581
Very good.

324
00:17:21,581 --> 00:17:26,647
The sales department has performed really well this time.

325
00:17:26,647 --> 00:17:28,947
Both offensively and defensively, right?

326
00:17:28,947 --> 00:17:32,147
Knowing how to sell houses and how to provide after-sales service

327
00:17:32,147 --> 00:17:35,214
is the long-term way to manage customers.

328
00:17:35,214 --> 00:17:40,448
Manager Gao, your all-around strategy this time was really comprehensive.

329
00:17:40,448 --> 00:17:42,381
It's great.

330
00:17:43,314 --> 00:17:46,281
Actually, it's not just my credit.

331
00:17:46,281 --> 00:17:49,081
The sustainable housing app was Cindy's idea.

332
00:17:49,081 --> 00:17:51,514
And she was also responsible for leading the project.

333
00:17:51,514 --> 00:17:55,947
We've all worked together as a whole department to achieve this.

334
00:17:56,647 --> 00:17:58,547
Don't be so modest.

335
00:17:58,547 --> 00:18:00,448
Although Cindy performed very well,

336
00:18:00,448 --> 00:18:04,682
it should also be credited to your leadership and empathy.

337
00:18:04,682 --> 00:18:07,581
The vice president position belongs to you for sure.

338
00:18:07,581 --> 00:18:11,648
I have high hopes for you. I look forward to your performance.

339
00:18:11,648 --> 00:18:13,248
Thank you, President, for giving me this opportunity.

340
00:18:13,248 --> 00:18:15,414
I will definitely work hard.

341
00:18:16,714 --> 00:18:18,781
Zhou,

342
00:18:18,781 --> 00:18:23,147
you should also seize the opportunity to assist your Vice President Gao well.

343
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:27,015
Yes.

344
00:18:27,015 --> 00:18:29,781
But don't work too hard.

345
00:18:29,781 --> 00:18:35,114
Seeing the employees happy and joyful is what I really want.

346
00:18:35,114 --> 00:18:38,114
I suggest you do your work well,

347
00:18:38,114 --> 00:18:41,015
and also maintain your relationship well.

348
00:18:41,015 --> 00:18:44,213
Get married earlier. Have a few more children.

349
00:18:44,948 --> 00:18:46,980
It was really well said, but President,

350
00:18:46,980 --> 00:18:48,748
you shouldn't talk much about such topics

351
00:18:48,748 --> 00:18:49,948
in the company now.

352
00:18:49,948 --> 00:18:52,581
They involve gender equality issues.

353
00:18:52,581 --> 00:18:55,380
It's so hard to chat in the office now.

354
00:18:55,380 --> 00:18:58,181
All right, let's not talk about this then.

355
00:18:58,181 --> 00:19:02,547
By the way, how do you feel about my arrangement of Cindy?

356
00:19:02,547 --> 00:19:05,648
Isn't it a little too harsh?

357
00:19:10,348 --> 00:19:12,114
Thank you.

358
00:19:16,047 --> 00:19:18,781
Take care, everyone.

359
00:19:18,781 --> 00:19:22,081
Sis, are you really going?

360
00:19:23,147 --> 00:19:25,815
Do you want to talk to the boss again?

361
00:19:25,815 --> 00:19:27,815
I didn't expect you to say yes.

362
00:19:27,815 --> 00:19:29,980
Not fun.

363
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:33,380
Sister Cindy, don't go. I'll talk to Uncle.

364
00:19:33,380 --> 00:19:35,915
The idea of the Sustainable Housing Maintenance App is yours.

365
00:19:35,915 --> 00:19:39,248
Even if you can't be the vice president, you can still be the manager.

366
00:19:39,248 --> 00:19:41,048
Forget it.

367
00:19:41,048 --> 00:19:44,082
I don't think the boss would

368
00:19:44,082 --> 00:19:47,047
want to upset a pregnant woman about the manager position.

369
00:19:49,682 --> 00:19:51,047
- What?
- Sister Yazi. You…

370
00:19:51,047 --> 00:19:54,214
That's right. I'm pregnant.

371
00:19:54,214 --> 00:19:55,481
Congratulations.

372
00:19:55,481 --> 00:20:00,781
As for the manager position, it's mine.

373
00:20:02,348 --> 00:20:05,280
All right, Cindy, wish you all the best.

374
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:08,747
- If you need any help, just let me know.
- Okay.

375
00:20:08,747 --> 00:20:11,347
Yes, Sister Cindy. Don't be shy, just let us know what you need.

376
00:20:11,347 --> 00:20:13,015
We're all rooting for you.

377
00:20:13,015 --> 00:20:18,148
- If so, I will count on you to handle these for me.
- No problem.

378
00:20:18,148 --> 00:20:21,414
Oh, I'm sorry, I can't handle this part.

379
00:20:21,414 --> 00:20:22,615
As for the self-contradictory part…

380
00:20:22,615 --> 00:20:23,948
As for the bulldozer part…

381
00:20:23,948 --> 00:20:25,914
Well, I'm pregnant.

382
00:20:25,914 --> 00:20:27,414
I'll do it.

383
00:20:27,414 --> 00:20:28,747
Can I touch it?

384
00:20:28,747 --> 00:20:30,813
It's just formed.

385
00:20:35,881 --> 00:20:39,081
This one, please help me handle this.

386
00:20:39,081 --> 00:20:41,682
See if there's anything you like, I'll give it to you.

387
00:20:41,682 --> 00:20:44,413
The rest, I'll trouble you as well.

388
00:20:44,413 --> 00:20:46,814
Idiot, I go to your house often.

389
00:20:48,081 --> 00:20:50,148
It's for you.

390
00:20:50,148 --> 00:20:52,748
New sprouts are growing.

391
00:20:54,214 --> 00:20:56,681
All right, bye.

392
00:21:00,281 --> 00:21:02,048
Do you have time to chat?

393
00:21:03,682 --> 00:21:05,115
Of course.

394
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,948
- Bye-bye.
- Bye.

395
00:21:31,648 --> 00:21:34,115
Wait! When it comes to helping someone,

396
00:21:34,115 --> 00:21:36,015
everyone has run away.

397
00:21:36,948 --> 00:21:38,860
No one is here.

398
00:21:38,860 --> 00:21:41,140
Okay, fine.

399
00:21:44,213 --> 00:21:45,848
This one.

400
00:21:46,815 --> 00:21:49,981
Just leave it. I'll do it.

401
00:22:18,014 --> 00:22:20,115
- You look…
- You look…

402
00:22:20,115 --> 00:22:22,514
- So familiar.
- So familiar.

403
00:22:45,614 --> 00:22:48,114
I didn't know you liked watching night scenery.

404
00:22:50,181 --> 00:22:52,647
I didn't know I liked watching night scenery either.

405
00:22:54,581 --> 00:22:58,380
Usually at this time, I'm either working overtime

406
00:22:58,380 --> 00:23:01,314
or on my way home from working overtime.

407
00:23:02,348 --> 00:23:04,414
I've never seen the night scenery.

408
00:23:05,147 --> 00:23:10,415
So, the night scenery is very novel to me.

409
00:23:12,348 --> 00:23:15,381
But if I had to choose again,

410
00:23:16,081 --> 00:23:18,480
I would still go back to work overtime.

411
00:23:20,447 --> 00:23:24,648
So am I the first person to watch the night scenery with you?

412
00:23:29,781 --> 00:23:33,580
Meng Heng, have you thought about your future?

413
00:23:34,181 --> 00:23:35,914
Yes, I have.

414
00:23:35,914 --> 00:23:37,747
But...

415
00:23:38,447 --> 00:23:42,813
I'm still figuring it out as I go.

416
00:23:44,914 --> 00:23:46,215
But don't worry.

417
00:23:46,215 --> 00:23:49,888
I'll make sure you live the life you want before I turn thirty.

418
00:23:58,481 --> 00:24:01,714
Do you know how old I'll be in eight years?

419
00:24:03,281 --> 00:24:05,047
Forget it, don't calculate.

420
00:24:05,047 --> 00:24:06,815
I don't want to know.

421
00:24:11,681 --> 00:24:16,982
Whether it's eight years or eighty years, you are still you.

422
00:24:17,781 --> 00:24:20,281
You will always be the Cindy I like.

423
00:24:27,248 --> 00:24:30,948
Do you remember the amusement park we went to before?

424
00:24:30,948 --> 00:24:34,313
Of course, I do. It was fun that day.

425
00:24:34,313 --> 00:24:37,248
Yes, it was very fun.

426
00:24:39,415 --> 00:24:41,647
But just after those happy days,

427
00:24:41,647 --> 00:24:44,980
you know, my hand hurt for three days.

428
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:46,748
Your hand hurt for three days?

429
00:24:46,748 --> 00:24:48,880
Why didn't you tell me?

430
00:24:49,547 --> 00:24:51,548
That's not the point.

431
00:24:52,914 --> 00:24:55,781
And it was at that time that I discovered,

432
00:24:55,781 --> 00:24:59,315
that our gap was not just in age,

433
00:24:59,315 --> 00:25:02,914
but also, in our planning for the future.

434
00:25:15,081 --> 00:25:17,381
Even if there is a gap,

435
00:25:18,514 --> 00:25:21,914
if there's anything you want me to do, I can accommodate you.

436
00:25:27,481 --> 00:25:30,348
But I can't stop and wait for you.

437
00:25:42,714 --> 00:25:47,881
But we are happy together, aren't we?

438
00:26:00,947 --> 00:26:04,514
Thank you. It was truly happy.

439
00:26:34,492 --> 00:26:38,491
♫ After a few ill-fated encounters ♫

440
00:26:38,491 --> 00:26:42,870
♫ I've long understood that there's no perfect match ♫

441
00:26:44,714 --> 00:26:46,647
By the way, Meng Heng,

442
00:26:49,081 --> 00:26:52,714
if you are willing, you are welcome to join my department after graduation.

443
00:26:52,714 --> 00:26:54,548
Let's work hard together.

444
00:26:54,548 --> 00:26:58,216
♫ Living a life that has nothing to do with me ♫

445
00:27:00,380 --> 00:27:02,514
I need to think about it.

446
00:27:04,181 --> 00:27:06,482
Because by that time,

447
00:27:06,482 --> 00:27:10,581
Sisters Yazi and Xiaoyun will definitely be fighting to have me.

448
00:27:11,547 --> 00:27:13,981
Because I will become very strong.

449
00:27:13,981 --> 00:27:16,212
♫ Stumbling and bumbling ♫

450
00:27:16,212 --> 00:27:17,581
Yes.

451
00:27:18,314 --> 00:27:20,547
You're amazing.

452
00:27:20,547 --> 00:27:22,681
You will definitely be in high demand.

453
00:27:23,596 --> 00:27:28,670
♫ Usually. Only folly is what can be picked up but not let go ♫

454
00:27:28,670 --> 00:27:31,581
I'm off. Bye.

455
00:27:31,581 --> 00:27:34,780
♫ Embracing the shape of bareness ♫

456
00:27:34,780 --> 00:27:37,030
Wait a moment.

457
00:27:48,013 --> 00:27:50,048
Can I hug you?

458
00:28:04,815 --> 00:28:08,082
If Zhang Shiping does wrong by you,

459
00:28:09,380 --> 00:28:11,448
you must tell me.

460
00:28:28,981 --> 00:28:32,147
Hurry up and leave. Go back quickly.

461
00:28:38,652 --> 00:28:41,876
♫ You say it's time to let go ♫

462
00:28:41,876 --> 00:28:45,162
♫ But I just can't learn to forget ♫

463
00:28:45,162 --> 00:28:48,681
♫ I have double standards ♫

464
00:28:48,681 --> 00:28:51,481
You wanted that lucky charm so much at that time.

465
00:28:51,481 --> 00:28:54,981
Look at how serious he is about you.

466
00:28:56,047 --> 00:29:01,780
Even if the method was not perfect, his intention was perfect.

467
00:29:04,580 --> 00:29:07,581
Don't you know I'm just a secretary?

468
00:29:07,581 --> 00:29:10,048
- I know that.
- You know that, yet you still chose me?

469
00:29:10,048 --> 00:29:13,114
You don't know the secretary's work is just to serve tea, deliver water, and do some unimportant tasks.

470
00:29:13,114 --> 00:29:14,648
Is this really what you want to do?

471
00:29:14,648 --> 00:29:17,148
So, the small tasks I do are also important.

472
00:29:17,148 --> 00:29:19,747
Or are you just saying it because it sounds good?

473
00:29:22,091 --> 00:29:25,197
♫ Highlighting oneself without discretion ♫

474
00:29:25,197 --> 00:29:28,914
♫ Can't tell reality from dreams ♫

475
00:29:28,914 --> 00:29:31,315
Why are you drinking alone here?

476
00:29:31,315 --> 00:29:33,115
Not really.

477
00:29:34,044 --> 00:29:36,514
♫ Presented me with a different chapter ♫

478
00:29:36,514 --> 00:29:38,581
Good night.

479
00:29:38,581 --> 00:29:40,681
What are you doing?

480
00:29:40,681 --> 00:29:43,081
I'll bring you somewhere.

481
00:29:43,081 --> 00:29:44,248
Where?

482
00:29:44,248 --> 00:29:45,947
You'll know once we get there.

483
00:29:47,458 --> 00:29:49,776
♫ I've entrusted myself to him ♫

484
00:29:49,776 --> 00:29:52,315
Whether to change or not is up to you.

485
00:29:52,315 --> 00:29:55,881
If you're unhappy with your job, change it for another one.

486
00:29:55,881 --> 00:29:57,281
You're so strong.

487
00:29:57,281 --> 00:29:58,714
Do you even know what you're doing?

488
00:29:58,714 --> 00:30:00,880
I do.

489
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:03,281
You protect Brother Yingjun, and I'll protect you.

490
00:30:03,281 --> 00:30:09,553
♫ As you turn around, there's a new journey ahead ♫

491
00:30:09,553 --> 00:30:12,583
♫ I'm still standing here responding ♫

492
00:30:12,583 --> 00:30:16,855
♫ The eternal self-questioning ♫

493
00:30:16,855 --> 00:30:20,114
If you really don't get along with him, just don't do it.

494
00:30:22,148 --> 00:30:26,280
You have an unpleasant experience with him, but why do you feel that I'm like him?

495
00:30:26,315 --> 00:30:28,547
I'm not like him.

496
00:30:31,547 --> 00:30:34,448
I'm afraid if I don't say it now, I won't have a chance.

497
00:30:34,448 --> 00:30:37,048
You don't have to give me an answer now.

498
00:30:37,048 --> 00:30:39,681
I can give you an answer right now.

499
00:30:39,681 --> 00:30:42,847
It's impossible for us.

500
00:30:42,847 --> 00:30:48,978
♫ The one who loved out of their league ♫

501
00:30:48,978 --> 00:30:51,851
♫ Highlighting oneself without discretion ♫

502
00:30:51,854 --> 00:30:54,598
♫ It's wrong ♫

503
00:30:54,598 --> 00:30:57,454
♫ The role of a passing character ♫

504
00:30:57,454 --> 00:31:01,511
♫ You won't miss me as one ♫

505
00:31:01,511 --> 00:31:08,094
♫ As you turn around, there's a new journey ahead ♫

506
00:31:08,094 --> 00:31:10,924
♫ I'm still standing here responding ♫

507
00:31:10,924 --> 00:31:13,496
♫ The eternal self-questioning ♫

508
00:31:13,496 --> 00:31:19,417
♫ I end up laughing when I want to cry ♫

509
00:31:20,747 --> 00:31:22,714
What are you doing here?

510
00:31:39,348 --> 00:31:42,248
Guo, don't be reckless.

511
00:31:42,313 --> 00:31:45,448
Be gentle with your movements. They are all sleeping.

512
00:31:45,448 --> 00:31:48,747
Let me tell you. Asking us to work overtime at night to move these things,

513
00:31:48,747 --> 00:31:50,980
we could make a complaint to the labor department.

514
00:31:50,980 --> 00:31:52,381
